'''Schingas''' were large, predatory, serpents native to [[Makem Te/Legends|Makem Te]]. There were several subspecies of these serpents, the most famous and prized of which was the 'serpent-stallion' [[schinga shikou]]. These serpents were used as mounts by the [[Swokes Swokes/Legends|Swokes Swokes]]. Other species included the [[schinga equa]], the [[schinga klaug]] (a subterranean breed), the [[schinga picai]] (a very small breed), and the [[schinga ikkow]] (a venomous variety).

